      "message": "Case when this is necessary:\n\nIF there is 1+ transactional task that requires sweeping AND empty TQ scheduler,\nTHEN tq.Run will just hang and never call tqtesting.StopAfter.\nHENCE, Yes.\n\nHowever,\nIF *only* RunUntil is used to run with flaky datastore,\nTHEN indeed `tqtesting.StopAfter` will be executed,\nTHEN indeed sweep will get eventually called strictly *after* a task that might have left something to sweep\nTHEN indeed sweep here isn\u0027t necessary.\n\nI choose to sweep here because sweeping is safer wrt future modifications.",
